<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.10.4">
<l>tēṉuka ṉāvi cekuttu paṉaṅkaṉi</l>
<l>tāṉeṟin tiṭṭa taṭamperun tōḷiṉāl</l>
<l>vāṉavar kōṉviṭa vanta maḻaitaṭuttu</l>
<l>āṉirai kāttāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum</l>
<l rend="indent">avaiyuyyak koṇṭāṉā liṉṟumuṟṟum.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With the huge, broad arms that threw Dhenuka</l>
<l rend="indent">onto the palm-fruit, destroying [his] life,</l>
<l>[he] blocked the rains that came</l>
<l rend="indent">as dispatched by the king of celestials [Indra],</l>
<l>Because of him who protected the cow herd,</l>
<l rend="indent">now we are at our end.</l>
<l>Because of he who took [them] to save them,</l>
<l rend="indent">now we are at our end.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
